        PA_CQ["<b><i><u>Joern CPG Engine · Taint Analysis</u></i></b>\nBuilds Universal Code Property Graph (CPG) from changed files · Apache 2.0\nLanguage support: C/C++ · Java/Kotlin · Python · JS/TS · Go · Ruby · PHP\nTaint query layer: source → sanitizer → sink traversal across CPG\nCPG output shared with Path B — call graph and reachability data\navailable to Heuristic Targeting and Call Graph nodes without re-parse\nApproach 3+: Fraunhofer-AISEC/cpg adds pluggable frontends (Rust · Kotlin · Swift)\nReplaces CodeQL — CPG taint covers same scope with no per-scan database build step\nRuns in parallel with Semgrep + ast-grep"]
